data.title: Ethermon District - Player & Guild House
data.description: Ethermon is a role-playing, play-to-earn game that offers a decentralized world of Ether monsters built on the Ethereum blockchain. It was the first PVP battle game on Ethereum, minting the first collection of Ether monsters NFTs or “Mons” in 2017. The game was taken over by its most dedicated players and an expanded team in 2019. Ethermon is now an entire game ecosystem, spanning from gameplay and a marketplace on Ethermon Classic to an MMO-inspired game in the Ethermon District — the largest gaming district in Decentraland.

data.description: Tommy Hilfiger returns to Metaverse Fashion Week hosting a four-day program centered around fashion, art and innovation with a selection of culture shapers in the Web3 space. Metaverse Fashion Week takes place from March 28th to March 31st, a new experience will be unlocked each day. TOMMY HILFIGER will work with metafashion leaders DRESSX and artist Vinnie Hager to inspire self-expression in the digital world, as well as hosting immersive experiences, and creating purchasable digital wearables and limited-edition NFTs.

Please take your time to wander around and discover the many pieces of art tucked away throughout our grounds.
Take the lift up to Amalgam and check out our wearables in the M3 boutique, grab a bite to eat,and a nice cup of coffee.
After that why not get a tattoo and hit the open mic in the beer garden?
Wander up the stairs into The Higline and enjoy the wonderful monthly rotating art collection curated by the amazing @iambenthomas
Then hit up our bar and lounge along with our rooftop VIP section
